{"tid":1639294,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【極重要】唔好再打跨區喇！係打就開花！","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:12:07.000Z","uid":177082,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"61c0c215b2d8c7ee4f4faa6162972166ca07418a","tid":1639294,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"KT9014的士乘客離奇失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1635791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1635791</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n除咗呢單外已經有夠多黑警攔截小巴巴士、甚至扮義載拉手足！<br />\n除非有Safe House 如果唔係嘅話 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">跨區風險極高</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係自己區開花就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算無黨鐵 無巴士 無任何交通工具 你都可以用雙腳係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">短時間內返到屋企</span></span><br />\n而且係自己區一定熟路 點樣走 走去邊 大家心裡有數<br />\n<br />\n係自己區Hit n Run 唔打陣地 搞掂即閃<br />\n唔洗戴好多Gear 輕裝就ok<br />\n啲狗接報到場已經走曬變返普通街坊<br />\n<br />\n比起跨區 係自己區開花<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">低成本 低風險</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗唔到有咩理由仲要堅持跨區陣地 然後等大搜捕<br />\n<br />\n我地每日被人拉咁多手足 仲要咁多屍體發現<br />\n我真係唔想大家再冒咁大風險<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港人 一個都不能少</span></span><br />\n唔係口講就係㗎 係真係要做出黎<br />\n<br />\n就算你已經豁出去 可以捨命 犧牲自己嘅嘢<br />\n但係唔係白白犧牲<br />\n<br />\n無錯 開花都有開花嘅危險<br />\n但係相比跨區 至少少咗回程嗰段時間要冒嘅風險<br />\n<br />\n如果認同麻煩真係幫手推推Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日見到咁多新聞我真係好心痛"},{"pid":"bc5363dd43d9c99064e06f4a8a5652ef3ab2313e","tid":1639294,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed0bb8f5e0cecef962610d38c2304c3b8f46b0f","tid":1639294,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a6ec2d98bac7bd12393246f0a9504e1a3258c7","tid":1639294,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:51:28.000Z","msg":"好心痛"},{"pid":"7355451b5fff4fe13e9195223a06bcbab5875d9e","tid":1639294,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"唔推喇 好撚攰 <br />\n是但啦"},{"pid":"0e83a0af2775c50b8e05250c646f2d05f187b42f","tid":1639294,"uid":155943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂住樓主"},{"pid":"1e8c2c36cd73f958f6f97c842e3e82c51e71f91e","tid":1639294,"uid":277010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61c0c215b2d8c7ee4f4faa6162972166ca07418a","tid":1639294,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"KT9014的士乘客離奇失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1635791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1635791</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n除咗呢單外已經有夠多黑警攔截小巴巴士、甚至扮義載拉手足！<br />\n除非有Safe House 如果唔係嘅話 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">跨區風險極高</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係自己區開花就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算無黨鐵 無巴士 無任何交通工具 你都可以用雙腳係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">短時間內返到屋企</span></span><br />\n而且係自己區一定熟路 點樣走 走去邊 大家心裡有數<br />\n<br />\n係自己區Hit n Run 唔打陣地 搞掂即閃<br />\n唔洗戴好多Gear 輕裝就ok<br />\n啲狗接報到場已經走曬變返普通街坊<br />\n<br />\n比起跨區 係自己區開花<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">低成本 低風險</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我諗唔到有咩理由仲要堅持跨區陣地 然後等大搜捕<br />\n<br />\n我地每日被人拉咁多手足 仲要咁多屍體發現<br />\n我真係唔想大家再冒咁大風險<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港人 一個都不能少</span></span><br />\n唔係口講就係㗎 係真係要做出黎<br />\n<br />\n就算你已經豁出去 可以捨命 犧